Package io.github.eingruenesbeb.yolo

package io.github.eingruenesbeb.yolo
This package is the main package for the minecraft server plugin "Yolo". It is licensed under the GPL-3.0-or-later license.

    io.github.eingruenesbeb.yolo.commands

    This package contains various utility classes called "managers", which each handle a respective aspect of the plugin.
